EasyJet Founder to Launch U.K. No-Frills Gym Chain, Times Says

-- B y   J o h n   S i m p s o n
-- 
2011-04-05T00:57:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-05/easyjet-founder-to-launch-u-k-no-frills-gym-chain-times-says.html
Stelios Haji-Ioannou, the founder of
 EasyJet Plc (EZJ) , is setting up easyGym, a chain of low-cost, low-
frills gymnasiums in the U.K., with Fore Fitness, which is
backed by venture-capital firm Fore Capital Partners, the
London-based Times reported, citing Paul Lorimer-Wing, the joint
chief executive officer of easyGym.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
